 Purpose:
Scrape logs for Grafana dashboard

Access Information:
- URL: http://mntr.lab.local
- Location (VM): mntr.lab.local
- Container/Service Name: Loki (docker container)

Credentials:
- Admin Username: n/a
- Admin Password Location: n/a

Technical Details:
- Database: n/a
- Configuration Files: /opt/docker/loki-config.yml
- Data Location: /var/lib/docker/volumes/loki-data/_data/
- Log Location: docker logs loki

Common Operations:

Restart:
docker compose restart loki

View Logs:
docker logs loki

Check Status:
docker ps | loki

Backup:
docker compose stop loki
sudo tar -czf /opt/backups/loki-$(date +%Y%m%d).tar.gz \
/var/lib/docker/volumes/loki-data/_data/>
docker compose start loki

Dependencies:
- Requires: n/a
- Required by: grafana

Notes:
- scraps logs, like prometheus but logs 
